TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Intelligence confirms that the enemy has left behind a vast energy production facility on the southern plane. We believe it is deserted but guarded by strong defensive towers. Find the facility and destory it!

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: This is a nanolathe. Set it to patrol and it will help nearby construction/factories.
You can build nanolathes with any tech 1 constructor.
This is an advanced solar collector. It produces lots of energy but also costs lots of energy to build.
Adv solar collectors can be built by any tech 1 constructor.
